TRANSFORM PROPERTY:-
# The transform property applies a 2D or 3D transformation to an element.i.e; we'll be able to make an overlapping effect too on the element. This property allows you to rotate, scale, move, skew, etc., elements.
 There are many values:-
# translate(x,y); where x and y can be -x% or x% and -y% or y%. -ve means it will be moving to left or bottom and +ve means it will be moving to right.
